primary color {
    white
    light gray  #D3D3D3
}

accent color{
    electric blue #007BFF, emerald green #50C878
}

primary font{
    helvetical, arial
}

accent font{
    futura
    bebas neue
    montserrat
}

Background: White or light gray.
Text: Dark gray or charcoal for body text, with bright red or electric blue for headings or call-to-action buttons.
Highlight Sections: Use emerald green or another bold color to draw attention to important parts like your portfolio categories or featured projects.


These colors will provide a nice contrast: 
the light gray as a soft neutral background, 
electric blue for vibrant accents, and emerald green for added pops of creativity. 
You can use these to create a clean yet bold and engaging portfolio.

